### Test Authentication Example
### Use this with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### 1. Test Login (Development/Test Only)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/test-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "testSecret": "your-test-secret-here"
}

### 2. Check if authenticated - Get current user
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/me
Cookie: access_token=<token-from-response>

### 3. Access a protected route (example)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/dashboard
Cookie: access_token=<token-from-response>
